test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1 NORMCOG
short_desc: If NORMCOG = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 1
full_desc: If Form D1, Q2. NORMCOG (participant have unimpaired cognition & behavior) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 1 (cognitively stable)

test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1 MCIAMEM, MCIAPLUS, MCINON1, MCINON2
short_desc: If MCIAMEM= 1 or MCIAPLUS=1 or MCINON1=1 or MCINON2=1, then DSCOGST should equal 2
full_desc: If any of Form D1 Q5a. MCIAMEM (amnestic MCI, single domain) or Q5b. MCIAPLUS (amnestic MCI, multiple domains) or Q5c. MCINON1 (non-amnestic MCI, single domain) or Q5d. MCINON2 (non-amnestic MCI, multiple domains) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 2 (MCI - DS)
test_logic: If (MCIAMEM= 1 or MCIAPLUS=1 or MCINON1=1 or MCINON2=1) and DSCOGST ne 2

test_name: DSCOGST compared to Form D1 DEMENTED
short_desc: If DEMENTED = 1, then DSCOGST should equal 3
full_desc: If Form D1, Q3. DEMENTED (participant meet criteria for dementia) = 1 (yes), then Q6. DSCOGST (What is the participant’s cognitive status?) should equal 3 (Dementia)
